            <link rel="alternate" href="https://ourworldindata.org/peak-agriculture-land"/>
            <published>2022-05-30T10:00:00.000Z</published>
            <updated>2022-06-02T19:22:49.000Z</updated>
            <author><name>Hannah Ritchie</name></author>
            <summary><![CDATA[The world produces more food than ever, but the amount of land we use is now falling. This means we can feed more people while restoring wild habitat.<br><br><a href="https://ourworldindata.org/peak-agriculture-land" target="_blank"><img src="https://ourworldindata.org/app/uploads/2022/03/peak-land-thumbnail-768x301.png"/></a>]]></summary>
